    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation level for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped to Gradation 1 and satisfied by existing documentation. The boundary-condition dataset (dataVintage 2025-10-24) predates the model revision of 2025-11-14 by 21 days; the team determined that the revision (trailing-edge chamfer refinement) does not affect fluid property inputs and accepted the dataset as current without commissioning a formal re-validation cycle. On this basis, the overall credibility package is accepted as sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision.",
